            Focus on passive stretching. Try Low Lunge (Anjaneyasana) to open up tight hip flexors, Half Splits (Ardha Hanumanasana) for hamstrings, and Thread the Needle for tight shoulders and upper back.
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-10 mb-4">Nervous System Integration</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            End your sequence with 3 minutes of Savasana, breathing slowly. This signals to your body that the stress of the workout is over, transitioning your system into a state of growth and recovery.
          </p>
        `
      }
    },
    { 
      params: { slug: 'surya-namaskar-beginners-guide' },
      props: {
        title: "A Complete Beginner's Guide to Surya Namaskar",
        category: "Poses",
        publishDate: "June 09, 2026",
        readTime: "9 min read",
        excerpt: "Honoring the sun. Learn the 12 sequential postures of Sun Salutations A, focusing on breath synchronization and fluid, graceful transitions.",
        coverColor: "from-[#FFF9FB] to-[#D9B8FF]/20",
        imagePath: "images/blog/sun_salutations_guide.png",
        content: `
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6 font-medium italic border-l-4 border-brand-primary pl-4">
            Surya Namaskar, or Sun Salutation, is a sequence of 12 powerful yoga poses that provides a complete cardiovascular and flexibility workout.
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-10 mb-4">The Benefits of Sun Salutations</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Sun Salutations stretch and strengthen all major muscle groups, improve blood circulation, stimulate digestive organs, and synchronize breath with movement for meditative focus.
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-10 mb-4">Breath Synchronization</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Each movement in the sequence is paired with an inhalation or exhalation. For instance, inhale as you reach up (Urdhva Hastasana), and exhale as you fold forward (Uttanasana).
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-10 mb-4">Tips for Beginners</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Move slowly and listen to your body. Modify poses as needed—use Cobra Pose instead of Upward-Facing Dog, or drop your knees to the mat during Chaturanga Dandasana.
          </p>
        `
      }
    }
  ];
}

const { title, category, publishDate, readTime, excerpt, coverColor, content, imagePath } = Astro.props;
const basePath = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title={title} description={excerpt}>
  <!-- Reading Progress Bar -->
  <div class="fixed top-20 left-0 right-0 h-1 z-50 bg-secondary-bg">
    <div id="reading-bar" class="h-full bg-brand-primary w-0 transition-all duration-75"></div>
  </div>

  <article class="bg-primary-bg py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Article Header -->
      <div class="space-y-6 text-center mb-12">
        <a href={`${basePath}blog`} class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-primary hover:text-btn-hover transition-colors">
          <svg class="h-4 w-4 mr-1.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          <span>Back to Blog</span>
        </a>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-3 text-xs text-text-secondary">
          <span class="bg-white border border-border-main rounded-full py-1 px-3.5 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-primary">{category}</span>
          <span>{publishDate}</span>
          <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-border-main"></span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main tracking-tight leading-tight max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          {title}
        </h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Banner Image Visual -->
      <div class="w-full h-64 sm:h-96 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-border-main mb-12 relative shadow-sm">
        {imagePath ? (
          <img 
            src={`${basePath}${imagePath}`} 
            alt={title} 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        ) : (
          <div class={`w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-tr ${coverColor} flex items-center justify-center p-8 relative`}>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(#e8afc7_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:24px_24px] opacity-15"></div>
            <svg class="h-32 w-32 text-brand-primary/45 drop-shadow-md" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2C11.5 5 9.5 8 6 8.5C7.5 10 7.5 12 7 13.5C8.5 13 10.5 13.5 12 16.5C13.5 13.5 15.5 13 17 13.5C16.5 12 16.5 10 18 8.5C14.5 8 12.5 5 12 2Z" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        )}
      </div>

      <!-- Article Layout -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <!-- Sticky Left sidebar: Table of Contents & Share -->
        <aside class="lg:col-span-3 lg:sticky lg:top-44 space-y-8 hidden lg:block">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-xs uppercase font-bold text-text-main tracking-wider border-b border-border-main pb-2">Contents</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-xs text-text-secondary font-medium" id="toc">
              <!-- Dynamically built TOC placeholders -->
              <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-brand-primary block transition-colors">Introduction</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-brand-primary block transition-colors">Core Exercises</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-brand-primary block transition-colors">Mindful Practices</a></li>
              <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-brand-primary block transition-colors">Routine Integration</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3.5">
            <h3 class="text-xs uppercase font-bold text-text-main tracking-wider border-b border-border-main pb-2">Share</h3>
            <div class="flex space-x-3">
              <button class="p-2 bg-white border border-border-main hover:bg-secondary-bg rounded-full text-text-secondary hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors cursor-pointer" aria-label="Share on Twitter">
                <svg class="h-4.5 w-4.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
              </button>
              <button class="p-2 bg-white border border-border-main hover:bg-secondary-bg rounded-full text-text-secondary hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors cursor-pointer" aria-label="Share on Facebook">
                <svg class="h-4.5 w-4.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 12c0-5.52-4.48-10-10-10S2 6.48 2 12c0 4.84 3.44 8.87 8 9.8V15H8v-3h2V9.5C10 7.57 11.57 6 13.5 6H16v3h-2c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1v2h3v3h-3v6.95c4.56-.93 8-4.96 8-9.75z"/></svg>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <!-- Rich Text content -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-9 bg-white border border-border-main rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-sm leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base text-text-main space-y-6 max-w-none prose prose-indigo">
          <div set:html={content} />
          
          <!-- Call To Action Inside Post -->
          <div class="mt-12 bg-secondary-bg/50 border border-border-main rounded-2xl p-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
            <div class="space-y-1.5 text-center sm:text-left">
              <h4 class="font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-text-main">Ready to deepen your practice?</h4>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-secondary">Download our premium, comprehensive yoga calendars and guides.</p>
            </div>
            <a href={`${basePath}programs`} class="btn-primary py-2.5 px-6 text-sm shrink-0 whitespace-nowrap shadow-sm">
              Explore Programs
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- Reading Bar logic -->
  <script>
    const bar = document.getElementById('reading-bar');
    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      const scrollHeight = document.documentElement.scrollHeight - document.documentElement.clientHeight;
      const scrollPercent = (window.scrollY / scrollHeight) * 100;
      if (bar) {
        bar.style.width = scrollPercent + '%';
      }
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
